title: Where will Dez Bryant land, Are the Cowboys Good, Patriots Problems (Football 04/16)
description:
Will Brinson and Ryan Wilson are LIVE from Nashville, fresh off John Breech's wedding to dive into the full Dez Bryant saga. Did the Cowboys do Dez dirty with the way they released him? Should they have offered him a paycut? Where will he end up landing next year and will it be with an NFC East team? Are the Cowboys the worst team in the NFC East? The guys also break down Danny Amendola's comments about Bill Belichick and examine all the issues the Patriots are dealing with lately.
